entries.femaleVariant: You're looking at a real star!
Hm, you look the same as yesterday. Don't get ahead of yourself.
You don't know squat. I was in a braindance by a famous scroller!
Whoa! What'd you have to do? Did you have to learn a bunch of lines?
No. Just had to walk down the street, waving a big baseball bat.
But you don't even know how to play baseball.
Yeah, 'cause we don't have a field. But I still did great.
Out getting my big start, since you never gave me one. Straight from the Badlands to the bright towers.
Heh, you should be thanking me. If you started in those towers, you'd be sittin' in the columbarium now.
